The paper discusses machine learning and its failure modes, which are common topics in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions datasets and experiments involving computer vision (cs.CV) and security (cs.CR). Additionally, the proposed objective function and criterion are related to information theory, which is a topic in the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
